DESCRIPTIONS
============

Implement for a test, refer to file "requirement.pdf" for details.

REQUIREMENTS
============

* libtesseract-dev, v4
* tesseract-ocr, libleptonica-dev, pkg-config follow libtesseract.
* Python, v2 or v3
* poetry, v1.0.10

USAGE
=====

    $ poetry shell
    $ poetry install  # installing could be very slow
    $ mkdir tmp
    $ python main.py --output tmp/out --input sample/001.jpg
    $ python main.py --output tmp/out --input sample/004.png --verbose
